{"tid":2508351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人當年讀廢中學，依家叫做成功向上流動","createTime":"2021-04-28T16:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T18:18:56.000Z","uid":137220,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dfad43e3b3391ab9b33a54a1c0aa4d7b2ebd7645","tid":2508351,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"我先，以前老豆老母唔撚理<br />\n簡中學自己簡，我識條春<br />\n<br />\n結果去左間充滿新移民既學校<br />\n咁就7年，最青春果7年<br />\n<br />\nCE18分已經係全級第三高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAlevel合格但唔夠分<br />\n<br />\n自修多一年，碌到入大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係剛做野捱得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔覺意捱左差不多十年，結果依家都叫算有中產收入 <br />\n<br />\n黎緊再轉工，人工再多dd，突然諗起以前，覺得自己依家好彩。"},{"pid":"8472762bb52f5dd277bff92bfcb067af82d9ae61","tid":2508351,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c71d178edef7f5df0662731b0e4c0bbcfc329e","tid":2508351,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16:34:23.000Z","msg":"咩叫中產收入？有無睇毒男的一生？"},{"pid":"689ba2486ab7e31631da3cdf80e0df1a8da2e1ee","tid":2508351,"uid":137220,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f5c71d178edef7f5df0662731b0e4c0bbcfc329e","tid":2508351,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16:34:23.000Z","msg":"咩叫中產收入？有無睇毒男的一生？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:59:26.000Z","msg":"依家4xk，黎緊5xk以上<br />\n唔記得毒男的一生搵幾多"},{"pid":"8bef2f2329cefb5d28fcd5e7a590ea18e0d5bb7b","tid":2508351,"uid":374209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"689ba2486ab7e31631da3cdf80e0df1a8da2e1ee","tid":2508351,"uid":137220,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f5c71d178edef7f5df0662731b0e4c0bbcfc329e","tid":2508351,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16: